<doc f='llvm/llvm/lib/Target/PowerPC/PPCRegisterInfo.cpp' l='698'>/// lowerCRSpilling - Generate the code for spilling a CR register. Instead of
/// reserving a whole register (R0), we scrounge for one here. This generates
/// code like this:
///
///   mfcr rA                  ; Move the conditional register into GPR rA.
///   rlwinm rA, rA, SB, 0, 31 ; Shift the bits left so they are in CR0&apos;s slot.
///   stw rA, FI               ; Store rA to the frame.
///</doc>
